## KaraCos Web Platform Engine
## Template theme starting point :
## templates are rendered with this context :
## ${instance} = current KaraCos object instance
## ${form} = form for current action if any
## ${result} = result of current action if any
## a form for a given action of a given object is called with url (see details below):
## http://${instance.__domain__['fqdn']/${instance._get_action_url()}/${action.action}
##
## Common instance API :
## instance.__domain__ : KaraCos Domain instance containing current instance
## instance['childrens'] = dict data for an instance childrens, key: object name, value : object_id in db
## get a children instance with instance.db[instance['childrens'][NODE_NAME]]
## instance._get_action_url() : returns domain absolute url
##
##
##